Package: statetipd
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
 erlang | erlang-nox, erlang-base (>= 1:15.b), erlang-indira (>> 0.9.0),
 erlang-etoml
Recommends: python-statetip
Description: monitoring data store
 StateTip is a data store that remembers most recent states of monitored
 objects (servers, network links and equipment, availability of services,
 etc.) StateTip allows then to retrieve the data about specific object and
 list the objects the data was collected about.

Package: python-statetip
Architecture: all
Section: python
Priority: optional
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}
Provides: ${python:Provides}
Description: monitoring data store - command line client and Python module
 StateTip is a data store that remembers most recent states of monitored
 objects (servers, network links and equipment, availability of services,
 etc.) StateTip allows then to retrieve the data about specific object and
 list the objects the data was collected about.
 .
 This package contains command line client and Python module to interact with
 StateTip daemon.

Package: statetip-doc
Architecture: all
Description: monitoring data store - documentation
 StateTip is a data store that remembers most recent states of monitored
 objects (servers, network links and equipment, availability of services,
 etc.) StateTip allows then to retrieve the data about specific object and
 list the objects the data was collected about.
 .
 This package contains documentation for StateTip daemon and Python client
 module.
